---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Maritime Code - Boating Accident">
  <!-- Header -->
  <section class="bg-[#061126] text-white py-16 border-b border-gray-700">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-6xl" style="font-family: 'Handjet', monospace; image-rendering: pixelated; image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; image-rendering: crisp-edges; text-rendering: geometricPrecision; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">
          Maritime Code
        </h1>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-gray-400 font-mono">
          Terms of service and conference guidelines for all crew members
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Terms Content -->
  <section class="py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none">
        <div class="bg-[#061126] p-8 border border-gray-600">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6" style="font-family: 'Handjet', monospace; image-rendering: pixelated; image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; image-rendering: crisp-edges; text-rendering: geometricPrecision; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Conference Maritime Code</h2>

          <div class="space-y-8">
            <section>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Handjet', monospace; image-rendering: pixelated; image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; image-rendering: crisp-edges; text-rendering: geometricPrecision; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Captain's Orders</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4 font-mono">
                Effective Date: January 1, 2025<br/>
                Last Updated: January 1, 2025
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono">
                Welcome aboard the Boating Accident Conference! By purchasing a ticket, registering for the event, or participating in any way, you agree to abide by this Maritime Code. These terms govern your participation in our crypto conference voyage.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Handjet', monospace; image-rendering: pixelated; image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; image-rendering: crisp-edges; text-rendering: geometricPrecision; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Ticket & Registration Rules</h3>
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-white" style="font-family: 'Handjet', monospace; image-rendering: pixelated; image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; image-rendering: crisp-edges; text-rendering: geometricPrecision; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Boarding Pass Validity</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono">Conference tickets are non-transferable and non-refundable unless the event is cancelled. Each ticket admits one person only and must be presented for verification at registration.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-white" style="font-family: 'Handjet', monospace; image-rendering: pixelated; image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; image-rendering: crisp-edges; text-rendering: geometricPrecision; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Registration Requirements</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono">All attendees must complete registration with accurate information. False or misleading information may result in denied boarding or removal from the vessel.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-white" style="font-family: 'Handjet', monospace; image-rendering: pixelated; image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; image-rendering: crisp-edges; text-rendering: geometricPrecision; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Payment Terms</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono">All payments must be received in full before boarding. We accept traditional payment methods and select cryptocurrencies. Chargebacks may result in permanent banishment from future voyages.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Handjet', monospace; image-rendering: pixelated; image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; image-rendering: crisp-edges; text-rendering: geometricPrecision; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Code of Conduct</h3>
              <div class="bg-[#061126] p-6 border border-gray-600">
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-3" style="font-family: 'Handjet', monospace; image-rendering: pixelated; image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; image-rendering: crisp-edges; text-rendering: geometricPrecision; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Crew Expectations</h4>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-400 space-y-2 font-mono">
                  <li>Treat all crew members and speakers with respect and courtesy</li>
                  <li>No harassment, discrimination, or inappropriate behavior of any kind</li>
                  <li>No unauthorized recording or photography of sessions or attendees</li>
                  <li>Respect intellectual property and confidential information shared</li>
                  <li>No solicitation or unauthorized promotional activities</li>
                  <li>Follow all venue rules and local maritime regulations</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 font-mono">
                Violation of these guidelines may result in immediate removal from the conference without refund and exclusion from future Boating Accident events.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Handjet', monospace; image-rendering: pixelated; image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; image-rendering: crisp-edges; text-rendering: geometricPrecision; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Media & Content Usage</h3>
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-white" style="font-family: 'Handjet', monospace; image-rendering: pixelated; image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; image-rendering: crisp-edges; text-rendering: geometricPrecision; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Photography & Recording</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono">Official conference photography and video recording will take place. By attending, you consent to being photographed/recorded and the use of such content for promotional purposes.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-white" style="font-family: 'Handjet', monospace; image-rendering: pixelated; image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; image-rendering: crisp-edges; text-rendering: geometricPrecision; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Social Media Policy</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono">You may share your experience on social media, but please respect other attendees' privacy. Use the official hashtag #BoatingAccident2025 for maximum visibility.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Handjet', monospace; image-rendering: pixelated; image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; image-rendering: crisp-edges; text-rendering: geometricPrecision; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Liability & Risk</h3>
              <div class="bg-[#061126] p-6 border border-gray-600">
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-white mb-3" style="font-family: 'Handjet', monospace; image-rendering: pixelated; image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; image-rendering: crisp-edges; text-rendering: geometricPrecision; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Maritime Disclaimer</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4 font-mono">
                  While we strive to provide a safe and valuable conference experience, crypto investing involves risk, and market conditions can be as unpredictable as ocean weather.
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-400 space-y-2 font-mono">
                  <li>Conference content is for educational purposes only, not financial advice</li>
                  <li>Attendees participate at their own risk and responsibility</li>
                  <li>We are not liable for any investment decisions made based on conference content</li>
                  <li>Lost or stolen personal belongings are not our responsibility</li>
                  <li>Weather conditions or force majeure may affect the conference schedule</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Handjet', monospace; image-rendering: pixelated; image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; image-rendering: crisp-edges; text-rendering: geometricPrecision; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Cancellation & Changes</h3>
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-white" style="font-family: 'Handjet', monospace; image-rendering: pixelated; image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; image-rendering: crisp-edges; text-rendering: geometricPrecision; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Event Cancellation</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono">If we must cancel the conference due to circumstances beyond our control, ticket holders will receive a full refund or credit toward a future event.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-white" style="font-family: 'Handjet', monospace; image-rendering: pixelated; image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; image-rendering: crisp-edges; text-rendering: geometricPrecision; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Schedule Changes</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono">We reserve the right to modify the conference program, speakers, or venue as needed. Significant changes will be communicated to all registered attendees.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Handjet', monospace; image-rendering: pixelated; image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; image-rendering: crisp-edges; text-rendering: geometricPrecision; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Health & Safety</h3>
              <div class="bg-[#061126] p-6 border border-gray-600">
                <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4 font-mono">Your health and safety are our top priority during this maritime adventure:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-400 space-y-2 font-mono">
                  <li>Attendees must comply with all applicable health and safety regulations</li>
                  <li>If you feel unwell, please stay ashore for everyone's safety</li>
                  <li>Emergency procedures will be communicated during the opening ceremony</li>
                  <li>Medical assistance will be available throughout the conference</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Handjet', monospace; image-rendering: pixelated; image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; image-rendering: crisp-edges; text-rendering: geometricPrecision; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Governing Law</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono">
                These terms are governed by the laws of Finland and international maritime law. Any disputes will be resolved through binding arbitration in Finnish courts or through alternative dispute resolution methods.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4" style="font-family: 'Handjet', monospace; image-rendering: pixelated; image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; image-rendering: crisp-edges; text-rendering: geometricPrecision; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">Questions About the Code?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4 font-mono">
                If you have questions about these terms or need clarification on any maritime regulations, contact our legal crew:
              </p>
              <div class="bg-[#061126] p-4 border border-gray-600">
                <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono">
                  Email: legal@boatingaccident.fi<br/>
                  Subject Line: "Maritime Code Inquiry"<br/>
                  Response Time: Within 5 business days
                </p>
              </div>
            </section>

            <div class="border-t border-gray-600 pt-6">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic font-mono">
                By participating in Boating Accident 2025, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by this Maritime Code. Fair winds and following seas!
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>